      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a meticulously maintained vehicle that exemplifies mechanical reliability and sophisticated engineering. This unit has undergone a rigorous multi-point inspection to ensure all vital systems perform to our exacting standards. While displaying the minor aesthetic markers consistent with responsible previous ownership, the vehicle remains in commendable condition both internally and externally. This offering represents an exceptional opportunity for the discerning buyer seeking a dependable, high-performance vehicle that balances long-term durability with significant market value.",
      "price": 34900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
