    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a great car. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. Whether you're commuting or heading out for a weekend trip, this beauty is ready to hit the road with its next owner. It\u2019s got plenty of life left in it and drives like a dream! Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin\u2014I'd love to see it go to a good home!",
      "price": 32000.0,
