    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a 2002 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This unit remains mechanically stout, benefiting from a comprehensive double VANOS overhaul and a reinforced rear subframe to maintain structural rigidity under high-torque loads. The 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox offers precise engagement, paired with a factory M-variable limited-slip differential for optimal exit-corner traction. The chassis is well-sorted, utilizing refreshed bushings and updated dampers to preserve the sharp turn-in characteristics of the E46 platform. While the exterior shows honest road wear consistent with its mileage, the performance vitals are sound, including a recent cooling system refresh and a clear oil analysis report.",
